collectionMetadata.name: Number of Deaths and Top 10 Principal Causes
collectionMetadata.description:
Total number of deaths and principal causes of death

Death figures referred to the number of deaths registered during the year.

The Mortality Tabulation List of the International Classification of Diseases - Tenth Revision has replaced the Ninth Revision as the adopted code set for the derivation of causes of death w.e.f Year 2012.

Refers to the top 10 principal causes of death only.
